high_descs: Turn around and make a straight turn before proceeding to turn left towards the counter top.
Pick up knife from the counter top.
Turn around and walk to the sofa to your left.
Slice bed on the sofa
Taking back the knife after slicing the bread from the sofa
Pick up slice of bread from sofa
Head towards the door, then hang a left and go to the microwave.
Place bread in microwave and heat it and pick it back
Turn around and going straight, proceed to turn to the left towards the coffee table.
Place bread on the coffee table.
anns.task_desc: Slicing bread and heating it on oven to eat

high_descs: Turn right and head straight through the room until reaching the countertop on the right, then go down this path to the microwave.
Remove the knife from the microwave.
Walk back to where you started, then go to the bread opposite the TV.
Slice the loaf of bread on the couch.
Place the knife down on the sofa.
Pick up one slice of bread.
Return to the microwave.
Use the microwave on the bread and retrieve it.
Turn left to go towards the hallway, then take a right and walk down it, taking the first right, going towards the glass coffeetable at the end of the room.
Place the slice of bread down on the coffeetable.
anns.task_desc: Slice a loaf of Bread, microwave one slice of it, and place that slice on a CoffeeTable.

high_descs: Cross to the right. Continue right and turn left at the first entrance. Go straight until you reach the countertop. Turn right in front of the countertop.
Open the microwave. Remove the knife. Close the microwave.
Go ahead to the round bread. Turn left.
Cut 7 slices of bread.
Get rid of the knife from the sofa.
Get the first slice of bread.
Return to the microwave.
Open the microwave. Place the slice of bread on the left side. Close the microwave. Turn on the microwave for 4 seconds. Open the microwave. Take out the bread. Close the door.
Turn left, reach the wall and turn left. Continue and turn right at the first door. When you enter, turn left. Go ahead and then turn right. Then turn left. Go to the coffeetable.
Place the slice of bread on the coffeetable.
anns.task_desc: Cut a loaf of Bread into slices. Heat a slice and take it to a CoffeeTable.
